### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Login with local credentials
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Store the JWT token from the login response
@authToken = {{login.response.body.$.accessToken}}

### Test authenticated endpoint with JWT
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### OAuth2 Login URLs (open these in browser)
# Google Login
# http://localhost:8080/oauth2/authorize/google

# Facebook Login
# http://localhost:8080/oauth2/authorize/facebook